Title: All In
Plot: With an Armenian hit-man hot on their trail, the Strike team sweeps the streets of the Armenian community to find him before he finds them.  After catching a break, Aceveda's suspicions grow about the Strike Team's involvement with the Money Train robbery.  Meanwhile, Dutch and Claudette investigate a case that could repeal hundreds of convictions, which leaves Claudette having to choose between her conscience and her career.
GuestStars: David Rees Snell, Cathy Cahlin Ryan, Brian J. White, Michele Hicks, Stana Katic, Karmin Murcelo, Dominic Hoffman, Marcos De La Cruz, Anthony Azizi, Andrew Borba
